[{"id": 558491, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 434, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3661, "text": "Hamd, g\u00f6kleri ve yeri yaratan, iki\u015fer, \u00fc\u00e7er ve d\u00f6rder kanatl\u0131 melekleri el\u00e7iler k\u0131lan Allah'\u0131nd\u0131r; O, yaratmada diledi\u011fini artt\u0131r\u0131r. \u015e\u00fcphesiz Allah, her\u015feye g\u00fc\u00e7 yetirendir."}, {"id": 558492, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 434, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3662, "text": "Allah, insanlar i\u00e7in rahmetinden her neyi a\u00e7acak olsa, art\u0131k onu k\u0131s\u0131p-tutacak yoktur; her neyi k\u0131sar-tutarsa, art\u0131k onu da ondan sonra sal\u0131verecek yoktur. O, \u00fcst\u00fcn ve g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc oland\u0131r, h\u00fck\u00fcm ve hikmet sahibidir."}, {"id": 558493, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 434, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3663, "text": "Ey insanlar, Allah'\u0131n \u00fczerinizdeki nimetini an\u0131n. G\u00f6kten ve yerden sizi r\u0131z\u0131kland\u0131ran Allah'\u0131n d\u0131\u015f\u0131nda bir ba\u015fka Yarat\u0131c\u0131 var m\u0131? O'ndan ba\u015fka \u0130lah yoktur. \u00d6yleyse nas\u0131l olur da \u00e7evriliyorsunuz?"}, {"id": 558494, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3664, "text": "E\u011fer seni yalanl\u0131yorlarsa, senden \u00f6nceki el\u00e7iler de yalanland\u0131. (En sonunda b\u00fct\u00fcn) \u0130\u015fler Allah'a d\u00f6nd\u00fcr\u00fcl\u00fcr."}, {"id": 558495, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3665, "text": "Ey insanlar, hi\u00e7 \u015f\u00fcphesiz Allah'\u0131n va'di hakt\u0131r; \u00f6yleyse d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131 sizi aldatmas\u0131n ve aldat\u0131c\u0131(lar) da, sizi Allah ile (Allah'\u0131n ad\u0131n\u0131 kullanarak) aldatmas\u0131n."}, {"id": 558496, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3666, "text": "Ger\u00e7ek \u015fu ki, \u015feytan sizin d\u00fc\u015fman\u0131n\u0131zd\u0131r, \u00f6yleyse siz de onu d\u00fc\u015fman edinin. O, kendi grubunu, ancak \u00e7\u0131lg\u0131nca yanan ate\u015fin halk\u0131ndan olma\u011fa \u00e7a\u011f\u0131r\u0131r."}, {"id": 558497, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3667, "text": "O inkar edenler; onlar i\u00e7in \u015fiddetli bir azap vard\u0131r. \u0130man edip salih amellerde bulunanlar ise; onlar i\u00e7in de bir ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma ve b\u00fcy\u00fck bir ecir vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 558498, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3668, "text": "K\u00f6t\u00fc olarak i\u015fledikleri kendisine \u00e7ekici-s\u00fcsl\u00fc k\u0131l\u0131n\u0131p da onu g\u00fczel g\u00f6ren mi (Allah Kat\u0131nda kabul g\u00f6recek)? Art\u0131k \u015f\u00fcphesiz Allah, diledi\u011fini sapt\u0131r\u0131r, diledi\u011fini hidayete eri\u015ftirir. \u00d6yleyse, onlara kar\u015f\u0131 nefsin hasretlere kap\u0131l\u0131p gitmesin. Ger\u00e7ekten Allah, yapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 bilendir."}, {"id": 558499, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3669, "text": "Allah, r\u00fczgarlar\u0131 g\u00f6nderir, onlar da bulutu kald\u0131r\u0131r, b\u00f6ylece Biz onu \u00f6l\u00fc bir beldeye s\u00fcr\u00fckleriz, onunla, yeri \u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fcnden sonra diriltiriz. \u0130\u015fte (\u00f6l\u00fcmden sonra) dirilip- yay\u0131lma da b\u00f6yledir."}, {"id": 558500, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3670, "text": "Kim izzeti istiyorsa, art\u0131k b\u00fct\u00fcn izzet Allah'\u0131nd\u0131r. G\u00fczel s\u00f6z O'na y\u00fckselir, salih amel de onu y\u00fckseltir. K\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fckleri tasarlay\u0131p d\u00fczenleyenler ise; onlar i\u00e7in \u015fiddetli bir azap vard\u0131r. Onlar\u0131n tasarlad\u0131klar\u0131 'bo\u015fa \u00e7\u0131k\u0131p bozulur'."}, {"id": 558501, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3671, "text": "Allah sizi topraktan yaratt\u0131, sonra bir damla sudan. Sonra da sizi \u00e7ift \u00e7ift k\u0131ld\u0131. O'nun bilgisi olmaks\u0131z\u0131n, hi\u00e7bir di\u015fi gebe kalmaz ve do\u011furmaz da. \u00d6m\u00fcr s\u00fcrene, \u00f6m\u00fcr verilmesi ve onun \u00f6mr\u00fcnden k\u0131salt\u0131lmas\u0131 da mutlaka bir kitapta (yaz\u0131l\u0131)d\u0131r. Ger\u00e7ekten bu, Allah'a g\u00f6re kolayd\u0131r."}, {"id": 558502, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3672, "text": "\u0130ki deniz bir de\u011fildir. \u015eu, tatl\u0131, susuzlu\u011fu keser ve i\u00e7imi kolay; \u015fu da, tuzlu ve ac\u0131d\u0131r. Ancak her birinden taze et yersiniz ve tak\u0131nmakta oldu\u011funuz s\u00fcs e\u015fyalar\u0131n\u0131 \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131rs\u0131n\u0131z. O'nun fazl\u0131ndan araman\u0131z ve umulur ki \u015f\u00fckretmeniz i\u00e7in gemilerin onda (denizde) sular\u0131 yara yara ak\u0131p gitti\u011fini g\u00f6r\u00fcrs\u00fcn."}, {"id": 558503, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3673, "text": "(Allah) Geceyi g\u00fcnd\u00fcze ba\u011flay\u0131p-katar, g\u00fcnd\u00fcz\u00fc de geceye ba\u011flay\u0131p-katar; g\u00fcne\u015fi ve ay\u0131 emre amade k\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r, her biri ad\u0131 konulmu\u015f bir s\u00fcreye kadar ak\u0131p gitmektedir. \u0130\u015fte bunlar\u0131 (yarat\u0131p d\u00fczene koyan) Allah sizin Rabbinizdir; m\u00fclk O'nundur. O'ndan ba\u015fka tapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131z ise, 'bir \u00e7ekirde\u011fin incecik zar\u0131na' bile malik olamazlar."}, {"id": 558504, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3674, "text": "E\u011fer onlara dua ederseniz, duan\u0131z\u0131 i\u015fitmezler, i\u015fitseler bile size cevap veremezler. K\u0131yamet g\u00fcn\u00fcnde ise, sizin \u015firk ko\u015fman\u0131z\u0131 tan\u0131mayacaklard\u0131r. (Bunu her\u015feyden) Haberi olan Allah gibi sana (hi\u00e7 kimse) haber vermez."}, {"id": 558505, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3675, "text": "Ey insanlar, siz Allah'a (kar\u015f\u0131 fakir olan) muhta\u00e7lars\u0131n\u0131z; Allah ise, \u011eaniy (hi\u00e7bir \u015feye ihtiyac\u0131 olmayan)d\u0131r, Hamid (\u00f6v\u00fclmeye lay\u0131k)t\u0131r."}, {"id": 558506, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3676, "text": "Dileyecek olsa, sizi giderir (yok eder) ve yepyeni bir halk getirir."}, {"id": 558507, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3677, "text": "Bu, Allah'a g\u00f6re g\u00fc\u00e7 de\u011fildir."}, {"id": 558508, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3678, "text": "Hi\u00e7bir g\u00fcnahkar bir ba\u015fka g\u00fcnahkar\u0131n g\u00fcnah\u0131n\u0131 y\u00fcklenemez. E\u011fer y\u00fck\u00fc a\u011f\u0131r olan kimse (bir ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131) onu ta\u015f\u0131maya \u00e7a\u011f\u0131rsa, -bu, yak\u0131n-akrabas\u0131 da olsa- kendisine ondan hi\u00e7bir \u015fey y\u00fckletilmez. Sen, yaln\u0131zca gayb ile Rablerinden 'i\u00e7leri titreyerek-korkmakta' olanlar\u0131 ve dosdo\u011fru namaz\u0131 k\u0131lanlar\u0131 uyar\u0131rs\u0131n. Kim temizlenip-ar\u0131n\u0131rsa, art\u0131k o, kendi nefsi i\u00e7in temizlenip-ar\u0131nm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. Sonunda d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f Allah'ad\u0131r."}, {"id": 558509, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3679, "text": "K\u00f6r olanla (basiretle) g\u00f6ren bir de\u011fildir;"}, {"id": 558510, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3680, "text": "Karanl\u0131klarla ayd\u0131nl\u0131k,"}, {"id": 558511, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3681, "text": "G\u00f6lge ile s\u0131cakl\u0131k da."}, {"id": 558512, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3682, "text": "Diri olanlarla \u00f6l\u00fcler de bir de\u011fildir. Ger\u00e7ekten Allah, diledi\u011fine i\u015fittirir; sen ise kabirlerde olanlara i\u015fittirecek de\u011filsin."}, {"id": 558513, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3683, "text": "Sen, yaln\u0131zca bir uyar\u0131c\u0131s\u0131n."}, {"id": 558514, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3684, "text": "\u015e\u00fcphesiz Biz seni, hak ile bir m\u00fcjde verici ve bir uyar\u0131c\u0131 olarak g\u00f6nderdik. Hi\u00e7bir \u00fcmmet yoktur ki, i\u00e7inde bir uyar\u0131c\u0131 gelip-ge\u00e7mi\u015f olmas\u0131n."}, {"id": 558515, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3685, "text": "E\u011fer seni yalanl\u0131yorlarsa, senden \u00f6ncekiler de yalanland\u0131; el\u00e7ileri ise; kendilerine apa\u00e7\u0131k ayetler, sahifeler ve ayd\u0131nlat\u0131c\u0131 kitaplar getirmi\u015flerdi."}, {"id": 558516, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3686, "text": "Sonra Ben de o inkar edenleri yakalay\u0131verdim. Beni inkarlar\u0131 nas\u0131l oldu (onlar g\u00f6rd\u00fcler)?"}, {"id": 558517, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3687, "text": "Allah'\u0131n g\u00f6ky\u00fcz\u00fcnden su indirdi\u011fini g\u00f6rmedin mi? B\u00f6ylece Biz onunla, renkleri de\u011fi\u015fik olan meyveler \u00e7\u0131kard\u0131k. Da\u011flardan da beyaz, k\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 renkleri de\u011fi\u015fik ve siyah yollar (k\u0131ld\u0131k)."}, {"id": 558519, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3688, "text": "\u0130nsanlardan, hayvanlardan ve davarlardan da renkleri b\u00f6yle de\u011fi\u015fik olanlar vard\u0131r. Kullar\u0131 i\u00e7inde ise Allah'tan ancak alim olanlar 'i\u00e7leri titreyerek-korkar'. \u015e\u00fcphesiz Allah, \u00fcst\u00fcn ve g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc oland\u0131r, ba\u011f\u0131\u015flayand\u0131r."}, {"id": 558520, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3689, "text": "Ger\u00e7ekten Allah'\u0131n Kitab'\u0131n\u0131 okuyanlar, namaz\u0131 dosdo\u011fru k\u0131lanlar ve kendilerine r\u0131z\u0131k olarak verdiklerimizden gizli ve a\u00e7\u0131k infak edenler; kesin olarak zarara u\u011framayacak bir ticareti umabilirler."}, {"id": 558521, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3690, "text": "\u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc (Allah,) ecirlerini noksans\u0131z olarak \u00f6der ve Kendi fazl\u0131ndan onlara art\u0131r\u0131r. \u015e\u00fcphesiz O, ba\u011f\u0131\u015flayand\u0131r, \u015f\u00fckr\u00fc kabul edendir."}, {"id": 558522, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3691, "text": "Kendinden \u00f6ncekini do\u011frulay\u0131c\u0131 olarak sana Kitap'tan vahyetti\u011fimiz ger\u00e7e\u011fin ta kendisidir. \u015e\u00fcphesiz Allah, elbette haber aland\u0131r, g\u00f6rendir."}, {"id": 558523, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3692, "text": "Sonra Kitab'\u0131 kullar\u0131m\u0131zdan se\u00e7tiklerimize miras k\u0131ld\u0131k. Art\u0131k onlardan kimi kendi nefsine zulmeder, kimi orta bir yoldad\u0131r, kimi de Allah'\u0131n izniyle hay\u0131rlarda yar\u0131\u015f\u0131r \u00f6ne ge\u00e7er. \u0130\u015fte bu, b\u00fcy\u00fck fazl\u0131n kendisidir."}, {"id": 558524, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3693, "text": "Adn cennetleri (onlar\u0131nd\u0131r); oraya girerler, orada alt\u0131ndan bileziklerle ve incilerle s\u00fcslenirler. Ve orada onlar\u0131n elbiseleri ipek(ten)dir."}, {"id": 558525, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3694, "text": "Derler ki: \"Bizden h\u00fczn\u00fc giderip yok eden Allah'a hamd olsun; \u015f\u00fcphesiz Rabbimiz, ger\u00e7ekten ba\u011f\u0131\u015flayand\u0131r, \u015f\u00fckr\u00fc kabul edendir.\""}, {"id": 558526, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3695, "text": "\"Ki O, bizi Kendi fazl\u0131ndan (ebedi olarak) kal\u0131nacak bir yurda yerle\u015ftirdi; burada bize bir yorgunluk dokunmaz ve burada bize bir b\u0131kk\u0131nl\u0131k da dokunmaz.\""}, {"id": 558527, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3696, "text": "\u0130nkar edenlere gelince, onlar i\u00e7in de cehennem ate\u015fi vard\u0131r. Onlar i\u00e7in ne, karar verilir, ki b\u00f6ylece \u00f6l\u00fcversinler, ne de kendilerine onun azab\u0131ndan (bir \u015fey) hafifletilir. \u0130\u015fte Biz, her nank\u00f6r olan\u0131 b\u00f6yle cezaland\u0131r\u0131r\u0131z."}, {"id": 558528, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3697, "text": "\u0130\u00e7inde onlar (\u015f\u00f6yle) \u00e7\u0131\u011fl\u0131k atarlar: \"Rabbimiz, bizi \u00e7\u0131kar, yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131zdan ba\u015fka salih bir amelde bulunal\u0131m.\" Size orda (d\u00fcnyada), \u00f6\u011f\u00fct alabilecek olan\u0131n \u00f6\u011f\u00fct alabilece\u011fi kadar \u00f6m\u00fcr vermedik mi? Size uyaran da gelmi\u015fti. \u00d6yleyse (azab\u0131) tad\u0131n; art\u0131k zalimler i\u00e7in bir yard\u0131mc\u0131 yoktur."}, {"id": 558529, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3698, "text": "\u015e\u00fcphesiz Allah, g\u00f6klerin ve yerin gayb\u0131n\u0131 bilendir. Ger\u00e7ek \u015fu ki O, sinelerin \u00f6z\u00fcnde (sakl\u0131) olan\u0131 bilir."}, {"id": 558530, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3699, "text": "Yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde sizi halifeler k\u0131lan O'dur. \u00d6yleyse kim inkar ederse, art\u0131k inkar\u0131 kendi aleyhinedir. Rableri Kat\u0131nda kafir olanlara kendi inkarlar\u0131 gazabtan ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 artt\u0131rmaz ve kafir olanlara kendi inkarlar\u0131 kay\u0131ptan ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 artt\u0131rmaz."}, {"id": 558531, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3700, "text": "De ki: \"Siz, Allah'\u0131n d\u0131\u015f\u0131nda tapt\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131z ortaklar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 g\u00f6rd\u00fcn\u00fcz m\u00fc? Bana haber verin; yerden neyi yaratm\u0131\u015flard\u0131r? Ya da onlar\u0131n g\u00f6klerde bir ortakl\u0131\u011f\u0131 m\u0131 var? Yoksa Biz onlara bir kitap vermi\u015fiz de onlar bundan (dolay\u0131) apa\u00e7\u0131k bir belge \u00fczerinde midirler? Hay\u0131r, zulmedenler, birbirlerine aldatmadan ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 vadetmiyorlar."}, {"id": 558532, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3701, "text": "\u015e\u00fcphesiz Allah, g\u00f6kleri ve yeri zeval bulurlar diye (her an kudreti alt\u0131nda) tutuyor. Andolsun, e\u011fer zeval bulacak olurlarsa, Kendisi'nden sonra art\u0131k kimse onlar\u0131 tutamaz. Do\u011frusu O, Halim\u2019dir, ba\u011f\u0131\u015flayand\u0131r."}, {"id": 558533, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3702, "text": "Yeminlerinin olanca g\u00fc\u00e7leriyle, kendilerine bir uyar\u0131c\u0131-korkutucu gelecek olsa, \u00fcmmetlerinin herhangi birinden mutlaka daha do\u011fru olacaklar\u0131na dair, Allah'a and i\u00e7tiler. Ancak onlara bir uyar\u0131c\u0131-korkutucu geldi\u011finde (bu,) nefretlerinden ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 art\u0131rmad\u0131."}, {"id": 558534, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3703, "text": "(Hem de) Yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde b\u00fcy\u00fckl\u00fck taslayarak ve k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fc\u011f\u00fc tasarlay\u0131p d\u00fczenleyerek. Oysa hileli d\u00fczen, kendi sahibinden ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 sar\u0131p-ku\u015fatmaz. Art\u0131k onlar \u00f6ncekilerin s\u00fcnnetinden ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 m\u0131 g\u00f6zlemektedirler? Sen, Allah'\u0131n s\u00fcnnetinde kesinlikle bir de\u011fi\u015fiklik bulamazs\u0131n ve sen, Allah'\u0131n s\u00fcnnetinde kesinlikle bir d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f\u00fcm de bulamazs\u0131n."}, {"id": 558535, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3704, "text": "Yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde gezip dola\u015fm\u0131yorlar m\u0131 ki, kendilerinden \u00f6ncekilerin nas\u0131l bir sona u\u011frad\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 g\u00f6rs\u00fcnler; \u00fcstelik onlar kuvvet bak\u0131m\u0131ndan kendilerinden daha g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fcyd\u00fcler. G\u00f6klerde ve yerde Allah'\u0131 aciz b\u0131rakacak hi\u00e7bir \u015fey yoktur. \u015e\u00fcphesiz O, bilendir, g\u00fc\u00e7 yetirendir."}, {"id": 558536, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 440, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3705, "text": "E\u011fer Allah, kazand\u0131klar\u0131 dolay\u0131s\u0131yla insanlar\u0131 (azap ile) yakalay\u0131verecek olsayd\u0131, (yerin) s\u0131rt\u0131 \u00fczerinde hi\u00e7bir canl\u0131y\u0131 b\u0131rakmazd\u0131, ancak onlar\u0131, ad\u0131 konulmu\u015f bir s\u00fcreye kadar ertelemektedir. Sonunda ecelleri geldi\u011fi zaman, art\u0131k \u015f\u00fcphesiz Allah Kendi kullar\u0131n\u0131 g\u00f6rendir."}]